(Sword Alliance)

709
00:33:20,940 --> 00:33:23,860
So this is the legendary Sword Alliance?

710
00:33:24,220 --> 00:33:26,420
Looks more like a market to me.

711
00:33:28,100 --> 00:33:30,420
I heard they turned it into shops
long ago.

712
00:33:30,940 --> 00:33:32,620
It was the Sword Saint himself
who pushed for it

713
00:33:32,620 --> 00:33:33,860
