714
00:33:34,860 --> 00:33:37,100
Why does this place look so familiar?

715
00:33:37,420 --> 00:33:39,900
Slap a new sign on it
and it's basically the GFTA.

716
00:33:43,820 --> 00:33:44,820
You think every shop

717
00:33:44,820 --> 00:33:46,140
belongs to your family.

718
00:33:47,100 --> 00:33:48,500
What is that about?

719
00:33:48,500 --> 00:33:49,420
Stay away from me.

720
00:33:50,780 --> 00:33:52,340
I can't let anyone know I'm back.

721
00:33:52,540 --> 00:33:53,660
I need to stay undercover.

722
00:33:54,780 --> 00:33:56,540
Young master, you've returned.

723
00:34:01,700 --> 00:34:02,540
Zhuge,

724
00:34:02,940 --> 00:34:04,260
