726
00:34:05,500 --> 00:34:07,060
That disguise is totally useless.

727
00:34:07,940 --> 00:34:09,140
You two go look around.

728
00:34:09,140 --> 00:34:10,780
I'm gonna find my second uncle
and see what's up.

729
00:34:13,340 --> 00:34:14,420
Let's go explore.

730
00:34:46,620 --> 00:34:47,460
Uncle?

731
00:34:51,640 --> 00:34:52,920
Wait, you...

732
00:34:54,380 --> 00:34:55,220
It's me.

733
00:34:57,060 --> 00:34:58,180
Heng!

734
00:35:00,020 --> 00:35:01,340
You scared me!

735
00:35:01,980 --> 00:35:03,300
You're finally back!

736
